Source: tox-libconfig
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0), dpkg-dev (>= 1.16.1), bison, flex
Maintainer: Anton Batenev <antonbatenev@yandex.ru>
Standards-Version: 3.9.4
Homepage: http://www.hyperrealm.com/libconfig/

Package: tox-libconfig
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Architecture: any
Description: C/C++ configuration file library
 Libconfig is a simple library for manipulating structured configuration
 files. This file format is more compact and more readable than XML. And
 unlike XML, it is type-aware, so it is not necessary to do string parsing
 in application code.

Package: tox-libconfig-dev
Section: libdevel
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, tox-libconfig (= ${binary:Version})
Architecture: any
Description: C/C++ configuration file library
 Libconfig is a simple library for manipulating structured configuration
 files. This file format is more compact and more readable than XML. And
 unlike XML, it is type-aware, so it is not necessary to do string parsing
 in application code.
